(1, 'Ricardo Gonzalez', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'My name is Ricardo and I\'m an english teacher from Las Vegas, USA. My teaching approach is based on live conversation, so you learn things that you wouldn’t learn in textbooks. The main goal is to teach you how to speak and use English like a native!', '', 'imageSlider1.png', '', '', 1, 37, 1000, '7YkZwePHsTk', 'Las Vegas, USA', 0, '3ojh7wyjv5.mp3', 'uxhbtbkoz0.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'ricardo-gonzalez', '', '', '', '', 0, 19, '', '', ''),
(2, 'Amani Edwards', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hi, everyone! I think it’s very important to give students information about American history and culture as well as English grammar. My favorite method of teaching is discussion, because in this way people can train their listening and speaking skills.', '', 'imageSlider2.jpg', '', '', 1, 35, 1000, '', 'Atlanta, USA', 0, '67f5d6mlvr.mp3', 'imageBanner2.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'amani-edwards', '', '', '', '', 0, 20, '', '', ''),
(3, 'Eric Jensen', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hello, my name is Eric. I\'m from New Haven, CT, USA. I\'m a teacher of English at BigAppleSchool. I think the best way to learn Englsh is to improve your listening and speaking skills. If you have difficulties with pronunciation, don\'t understand native speakers accent or need to overcome a language barrier than study in BigAppleSchool is the best choice. ', '', 'rv54qztpda.jpg', '', '', 1, 59, 1000, 'l0OycVCahEw', 'Connecticut, USA', 0, 'ys287ctsu0.mp3', 'f5jdtq8jzu.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'eric-jensen', '', '', '', '', 0, 21, '', '', ''),
(18, 'Glenn Abson', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hello everybody! My name is Glenn and I truly believe that practicing with the native speaker of English can really help students to get through all difficulties with grammar, vocabulary and pronunciation. It is the best way to improve your language skills.', '', 'imageSlider18.jpg', '', '', 1, 41, 1000, 'Jbcnt7oGYpw', 'Leeds, UK', 0, 'ekfjkys35t.mp3', 'imageBanner18.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'glenn-abson', '', '', '', '', 0, 22, '', '', ''),
(20, 'Philip Jones', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'What\'s up world! My name is Philochko. I’m a native New-Yorker, living here, in Siberia. I like to show my students real life English, and I\'m going to teach you some slangs, idioms, and everything that you will never learn at your school or in the University.', '', 'imageSlider20.jpg', '', '', 1, 46, 1000, 'EECPeyUyypg', 'New York, USA', 0, '', 'imageBanner20.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'philip-jones', '', '', '', '', 0, 23, '', '', ''),
(21, 'Florian Fleury', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'My name is Florian, I’m from Rapperswil, Switzerland. I think that it is important when students are fully involved in the learning process. I adapt my method of teaching English according to the personal student’s needs to make it even more effective.', '', 'imageSlider21.png', '', '', 1, 48, 1000, '0GX3LRNwKtc', 'Rapperswil, Switzerland', 0, 'ohohi2cifm.mp3', 'lu3o56otkp.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'florian-fleury', '', '', '', '', 0, 24, '', '', ''),
(22, 'Catherine Richards', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hello, my name is Kate. I\'m from USA, but I\'m living in Cyprus. I\'m TEFL certified and majored in education. I really enjoy teaching people to speak English and love listening and talking to people from other countries. It is a lot of fun for me to help people express their ideas and emotions the way native English-speakers say things. I look forward to speaking with you!', '', 'nnsywcfupg.jpg', '', '', 1, 118, 10, '', 'Chicago, USA', 0, '1cj7t3kmpt.mp3', 'h6jne0ujsu.jpg', '', '', 3, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'catherine-richards', '', '', '', '', 0, 25, '', '', ''),
(23, 'Eon Adriaan', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hello, my name is Eon. I’m from Cape Town, South Africa and I’m TEFL & TESOL Qualified. I’ve been teaching English since 2007 and my experience includes teaching General and Business English for students from various levels and back grounds. During my free time I enjoy long distance running, reading, shopping, travelling and learning about new cultures. See you in my class!', '', 'sg4kcxmqmr.jpg', '', '', 1, 116, 10, '-ZTYx9QG3Wo', 'Cape Town, South Africa', 0, 'vpde00ca5e.mp3', 'oede2mwhwv.jpg', '', '', 3, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'eon-adriaan', '', '', '', '', 0, 26, '', '', ''),
(24, 'Maggie O\'Brien', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hello! My name is Maggie O’Brien. I am a native English speaker and a qualified TEFL instructor. I am from Ireland but now I live here in sunny Egypt! I love teaching online because it gives me the unique opportunity to speak with people from all over the world from my own home. My goal is to help you achieve yours. Sign up for a free trial with me today! Let’s learn and work together with BigAppleSchool.', '', 'w1f4d0hsxs.jpg', '', '', 1, 117, 10, '', 'Wexford, Ireland', 0, '179oeu6by2.mp3', 'yj9nsrn9u9.jpg', '', '', 3, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'maggie-obrien', '', '', '', '', 0, 27, '', '', ''),
(25, 'Hazel Gladys', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'My name is Hazel and I am your online English teacher. I have an IELTS certification. I have been teaching English for almost five years. I try to help my students improve English as a whole, in listening, reading, speaking and writing. I make every second count and teach with the best of my abilities. Well, I\'m looking forward to learn more about you and meeting you. See you in my class.', '', 'dzw9dosr93.png', '', '', 1, 115, 10, 'mP3y8nqVVJ0', 'Baguio, Philippines', 0, 'k5jlj1dcj5.mp3', 'hyl20kh0xj.jpg', '', '', 3, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'hazel-gladys', '', '', '', '', 0, 28, '', '', ''),
(26, 'Evanthia Stavrou', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hello, my name is Evita! I teach English for 10 years already! I am very aware of students’ difficulties in learning a foreign language. I like to teach English in context, enabling students to learn from actual language use and to practice meaningful conversation, my motto is \'\'Making learning English fun!\' I like reading , travelling, cooking and meeting new people. See you soon in my class!', '', '0mmepfz06p.jpg', '', '', 1, 119, 10, '', 'Thessaloniki, Greece', 0, '3zbaqg0qei.mp3', 'wdcf54mo8a.jpg', '', '', 3, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'evanthia-stavrou', '', '', '', '', 0, 29, '', '', ''),
(27, 'Zafar Saddique', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'My name is Zafar and I\'m a TEFL qualified teacher. I am a native of the UK. My aim as a teacher is to make sure my students improve and feel comfortable using the English language. My teaching method changes to suit students, as not all students are the same. I love team sports and football has always been my favorite. I hope to be teaching you very soon, have a great day!', '', 'mpf2ja4fcc.jpg', '', '', 1, 114, 10, '', 'Birmingham, UK', 0, 'ajeb16pxyn.mp3', 'j89gai1417.jpg', '', '', 3, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'zafar-saddique', '', '', '', '', 0, 30, '', '', ''),
(32, 'Piter Higdon', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'I\'m Peter, I grew up in Toronto, Canada. I\'ve tutored since high school, and I started teaching ESL in 2003. I\'ve taught in Brazil, China, Canada, and Turkey. I speak French, Spanish, and Portuguese. I believe in student centered learning because that\'s what works for me. I don\'t just teach English, I teach how to learn English. I teach in a goal-oriented style, working towards what is most important to you!', '', 'soxafcc6g8.JPG', '', '', 1, 58, 1000, 'JLYZa5Fc7ZA', 'Toronto, Canada', 0, '', 'ducl651j7h.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'piter-higdon', '', '', '', '', 0, 31, '', '', ''),
(33, 'Alex Mcgrath', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Greeting everybody! I enjoy meeting new people and helping them learn about American culture and the English language. I study Russian, and I can speak some German. No matter what your level may be – I look forward to see you at my classes!', '', 'imageSlider33.jpg', '', '', 1, 29, 1000, 'zyk7AuC4ZbY', 'New Hampshire, USA', 0, '', 'xnkxkwezba.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'alex-mcgrath', '', '', '', '', 0, 32, '', '', ''),
(34, 'Nishad Shambhusharan', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hello everybody! My name is Nishad Shambhusharan, I am from Mumbai, india.\r\nI know English, Hindi and Russian. As a Language teacher my aim is to give the best knowledge to my students to improve their English. I like to teach them in a funny way because this method works in a best way.', '', '8dy7lrkt3i.jpg', '', '', 1, 151, 1000, '', 'Mumbai, India', 0, '', 'i3jg3ii4k7.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'nishad-shambhusharan', '', '', '', '', 0, 33, '', '', ''),
(35, 'Michael Adio', 'Адио', 'Майкл', 'Майкла', 'Майклу Адио', 'Майклом', 'AqnYSlREoxs', '<p>Hello! I\'m an ESL teacher. I come to Novosibirsk from Nigeria, where English is the official language. I have been teaching English in Russia for 8 years and I consider teaching English to Russian students to be a great privilege.</p>', 'imageHeader35.svg', 'imageSlider35.jpg', '', '', 1, 23, 22, '', 'Jos, Nigeria', 8, 'fz7dg3xww4.mp3', 'imageBanner35.jpg', '', '', 2, '1', '0', '1', '1', 'imageBlogPreview35.svg', 'imageBlogHeader35.svg', 'imageBlogHeaderTeacher35.svg', 'imageFooter35.svg', 'imageFooterSm35.svg', 'imageFooterMd35.svg', 'imageTest35.svg', 'ogImage35.jpg', 'ogImagePost35.jpg', 'michael', '<p>В Новосибирск Майкл приехал из Нигерии. После окончания университета в своей родной стране, Майк получил приглашение на стажировку от Новосибирского Государственного Педагогический Университета и остался здесь жить. В 2013 году он получил квалификацию &laquo;Учитель английского языка&raquo; по специальности &laquo;Иностранный (английский) язык&raquo; в НГПУ.</p>\r\n<p>Майкл &mdash; позитивный и харизматичный преподаватель, который умеет завладеть вниманием и поднять настроение не только взрослых, но и&nbsp;детей любого возраста. И ему всегда есть чем поделиться со своими студентами.</p>', '', '', '42abd9', 140, 15, '', '', ''),
(37, 'Don Bello', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'My name is Don, and I am a CELTA certified teacher from Atlanta, Georgia. I create comfortable atmosphere and provoke speaking causing students to improve day by day. If learning English is your goal, then let us start this journey together at my classes!', '', 'imageSlider37.jpg', '', '', 1, 36, 1000, 'F-Y5zkZ_iHM', 'Atlanta, USA', 0, '', 'imageBanner37.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'don-bello', '', '', '', '', 0, 34, '', '', ''),
(38, 'Justina Means', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hi, my name is Justina, I\'m from Colorado. At my lessons I like using different modern techniques: watching movies, listening to music and practicing slang expressions. I think communication is one of the most important parts of studying. See you in class!', '', 'imageSlider38.jpg', '', '', 1, 39, 1000, 'wFOddDW41HQ', 'Colorado, USA', 0, '', 'imageBanner38.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'justina-means', '', '', '', '', 0, 35, '', '', ''),
(47, 'Christian Green', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hi, my name is Christian. I studied Russian at the USA, but I never had a chance to speak with native speakers of Russian. Here, in BigAppleShcool students have a chance to be surrounded with English. That’s what you need to be a master of language.', '', 'imageSlider47.jpg', '', '', 1, 45, 1000, '', 'California, USA', 0, '', 'imageBanner47.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'christian-green', '', '', '', '', 0, 36, '', '', ''),
(49, 'Patrick Meade', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hello! My name is Patrick, and I\'m from Buffalo. I\'m a native speaker of English and I really enjoy teaching people in Russia. I focus on making my students speak more, because the best way to study English is practicing. Come and try up my lessons!', '', 'imageSlider49.jpg', '', '', 1, 33, 1000, 'ky3qisPK0xc', 'Buffalo, USA', 0, '', 'imageBanner49.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'patrick-meade', '', '', '', '', 0, 37, '', '', ''),
(51, 'Adida Pir', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'My name is Maria Tereza, I am from Brazil and study International Relations.\r\nI\'ve lived in a few places already in the US, Europe and now here in Russia. I had some great adventures in all of them. Here in Novosibirsk I was adopted by BigAppleSchool and had a great time being a temporary teacher for them. Overall I found everything great here, beginning with the people up until to the cuisine. Hope to come back not only as a teacher but as a friend as well!', '', 'rdg8vukogx.jpg', '', '', 1, 152, 1000, '', 'India', 0, '', 'e81akltd25.jpg', '', '', 4, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'adida-pir', '', '', '', '', 0, 38, '', '', ''),
(53, 'Carlton McDonald', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'My name is Chris and I\'m an English teacher. I belive in treating every student as an individual and helping each of them in the method that suites them best. I belive learning a language is simple with the right guidance and support from the teacher. Thank you! And I look forward to hear from you.', '', '8vai6llsyk.jpg', '', '', 1, 113, 10, '', 'Stroud, UK', 0, 'zgcs12y29y.mp3', '27m4qs2jq1.jpg', '', '', 3, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'carlton-mcdonald', '', '', '', '', 0, 39, '', '', ''),
(54, 'Cecil Margarette', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hi, my name is Cecil and I\'m an English teacher. I belive that teaching students by way of creatinga fun is the most effective way of discovering and gaining knowledge. My classes are fun because I encourage them to speak out their opinions and ask them fun and nteresting questions. So what are you waiting for? Let\'s study and have some fun!', '', 'syah8yfw8y.jpg', '', '', 1, 112, 10, '', 'Manila, Philippines', 0, 'v0x58612b2.mp3', 'qg1f440avg.jpg', '', '', 3, '0', '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'cecil-margarette', '', '', '', '', 0, 40, '', '', ''),
